today. I solo'd through hell in 1 day in the Thurgadin mines and sold 14 heads. Time well spent if u ask me. Oh yeah, if u die, it's not a problem getting a rez either. U can probably bet u will be the lowest level player there. Everyone else seemed to be in the area of level 40 - 55 doing the shawl quest In Thurgadin.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Fantik Spelslinger<br>
